## ğŸŒ API Endpoints

### ğŸ” Authentication

* `POST /api/auth/register` â€“ Register new user
* `POST /api/auth/login` â€“ Login user
* `GET /api/auth/me` â€“ Get current user
* `POST /api/auth/logout` â€“ Logout user

### ğŸ§‘ Attendance (Employee)

* `POST /api/attendance/checkin` â€“ Check in
* `POST /api/attendance/checkout` â€“ Check out
* `GET /api/attendance/today` â€“ Today's status
* `GET /api/attendance/my-history` â€“ Attendance history

### ğŸ‘” Attendance (Manager)

* `GET /api/attendance/all` â€“ All employees' attendance
* `GET /api/attendance/report` â€“ Generate report
* `GET /api/attendance/calendar` â€“ Calendar data
* `GET /api/attendance/export` â€“ Export to CSV
* `GET /api/attendance/export-report` â€“ Export report to CSV

### ğŸ“Š Dashboard

* `GET /api/dashboard/employee` â€“ Employee dashboard stats
* `GET /api/dashboard/manager` â€“ Manager dashboard stats

